+.TH bcache-status 8
+.SH NAME
+bcache-status \- Display useful bcache statistics
+.SH SYNOPSIS
+.B bcache-status
+[\fB \--help\fR ]
+[\fB \-f\fR ]
+[\fB \-h\fR ]
+[\fB \-d\fR ]
+[\fB \-t\fR ]
+[\fB \-a\fR ]
+[\fB \-r\fR ]
+[\fB \-s\fR ]
+[\fB \-g\fR ]
+.SH DESCRIPTION
+This command displays useful bcache statistics in a convenient way.
+.SH OPTIONS
+.TP
+.BR \---help
+Print help message and exit.
+.TP
+.BR \-f,\ --five-minute
+Print the last five minutes of stats.
+.TP
+.BR \-h,\ --hour
+Print the last hour of stats.
+.TP
+.BR \-d,\ --day
+Print the last day of stats.
+.TP
+.BR \-t,\ --total
+Print total stats.
+.TP
+.BR \-a,\ --all
+Print all stats.
+.TP
+.BR \-r,\ --reset-stats
+Reset stats after printing them.
+.TP
+.BR \-s,\ --sub-status
+Print subdevice status.
+.TP
+.BR \-g,\ --gc
+Print subdevice status.
+
